    "description": [
      "Tall trees line both sides of a wide and rocky path, a mixture of grey-barked haon mingling with shingle monirs, quaking aspens, and silvery beeches to create a thick canopy overhead.  Slivers of moonlight strike the forest floor in thin beams, lending to the stillness of the setting, broken by the occasional hoot of an owl.",
